@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sfyuod(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.16 / v1 + 0.22)) / ((v0 + 0.89 / tmp + 0.22) * (v0 + 0.29 - tmp + 0.33)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v1 + 0.54 / v0 + 0.92)))
    v1 = wp.sin(0.14)
    v2 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.87 - v2 + 0.87)) * wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.37)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
